snippet.textDisplay:
Dot Rotten started all this off, and is killing everyone in Grime.
26+ songs/disses in the last month alone (at least 6 to Wiley, 2 to Jaykae, and 2 to Stormzy so far, however that's 8 songs in total not 10) with Wiley (twice) and Jaykae being the only big names to reply to Dot so far.
Most of them are too scared to reply to Dot as they know he'll rip them to pieces too.
He's set himself a target of at least 1 song/diss every single day in 2020. That sounds optimistic, but who knows how long he can keep it up.
snippet.textOriginal:
*Dot Rotten* started all this off, and is killing everyone in *Grime.* 
26+ songs/disses in the last month alone (at least 6 to Wiley, 2 to Jaykae, and 2 to Stormzy so far, however that's 8 songs in total not 10) with *Wiley* (twice) and *Jaykae* being the only big names to reply to *Dot* so far. 
Most of them are too scared to reply to *Dot* as they know he'll rip them to pieces too. 
He's set himself a target of at least 1 song/diss every single day in 2020. That sounds optimistic, but who knows how long he can keep it up.
